data.description: Welcome to this Charming Ranch style home on a Large Corner Lot located on the South side of Ottawa. Great Country Kitchen with a nice Dining room. Spacious Living room features a picture window that is perfect for letting in the natural sunlight. The 2 Bedrooms both have hardwood floors and nice large closets. Full Basement with Laundry room and plenty of storage. One Car detached garage and 12X32 Amish Made Shed with garage door. Enjoy your summers with the Fenced in yard with above ground pool and Amish Made Pool House (14X32) with 2 Lofts & a nice Front Porch. There is plenty of room for a large garden area. Updates Include: 2023 New Waterproof Laminate Floors in Living Room, Kitchen & Bathroom, 2021 New Roof on House, 2019 Added Public Water & Sewer, New Furnace, A/C, &  Fenced Yard, 2018 New Water Heater & Kitchen Appliances.
